name: Cacti Couple
description:
Art by AceWay

More info see Cacti Couple on LouBagel.com

Controls

  • Move Left/Right
    • Arrow Keys
    • A/D Keys (WASD)
  • Jump (Hold Jump Key to jump higher, aka jump sustain)
    • Up Arrow
    • W Key
    • Spacebar
  • Fire Jetpack
    • Up Arrow
    • W Key
    • Spacebar
  • Fullscreen
    • Tab
    • Escape to exit Fullscreen, at any time
